Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.59,0:00:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（ルフィ）『ワンピース』　１０周年！\N（一同）乾杯！\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.62,0:00:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,・『Ｓｈａｒｅ　Ｔｈｅ　Ｗｏｒｌｄ』\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.67,0:00:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,・～\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.82,0:00:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,・～\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:01:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,・～\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.56,0:01:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,・～\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.76,0:01:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,・～\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.96,0:02:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,・～\N
